      h3.title Uncoupled Networks
      p.projwords Loose coupling of components and data means interchangeable alternative implementations, to avoid misplaced restrictions relating to platform, programming language, operating system or supplier, which  clash with edge-based prerogative.  The oughtomation method implements “rules-as-data” with simple input/output control-tables that work with any programming language, given the accompanying parsing library. This avoids “rules as code” lock-in where algorithms are expressed in various incompatible procedural programming languages.
